User-Config-DB-Keyed version 0.01_01
====================================

To store the configuration-values for User::Config-users in a table of
an relational database, this backend can be used.

All values for all Users will be stored in the same database, indexed
by the username and the name of the option.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

User::Config
DBI

